title: Shania Twain...Come on Over(1999)[FLAC]
description:
Come on Over is the third studio album recorded by Canadian singer Shania Twain. It was released on November 4, 1997. It is the best-selling country music album of all time and one of the best-selling albums worldwide with sales of 39 million. Revised international version (1999)
The album was later re-released after the success of "That Don't Impress Me Much". This 'revised version' included the Notting Hill Remix for "You've Got a Way" and the (UK) Dance Remix for "That Don't Impress Me Much".
